{"tid":831893,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有冇gym room諗過進駐青衣？","createTime":"2018-09-22T10:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T22:48:31.000Z","uid":61091,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4c0f6d343da8df9ae8767fa72ca9e8da98f1b8aa","tid":831893,"uid":61091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T10:49:26.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆 青衣話大唔大 話細又唔細<br />\n單單係一個青衣島已經有3間康文署健身室<br />\n而且使用率亦都唔低 可見青衣撚對gym room係有一定需求<br />\n<br />\n但係對於玩開重訓嘅人嚟講 康記嘅gym根本達唔到最低要求(一個squat rack都冇)<br />\n如果要去玩啲好少少嘅gym 最近都要去到荃灣葵芳<br />\n企其實都好撚唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知p記 goji呢啲大gym會唔會考慮進駐青衣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60bc432ed2c4fdc8c4cc9a0f228932f0631464d","tid":831893,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:02:42.000Z","msg":"No<br />\n因為多公屋"},{"pid":"f677626c0c0042e8c4242fa1f4d0b24e114864ce","tid":831893,"uid":120791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"青衣體育館：算新但係個gym房細到on9 機少人多<br />\n<br />\n楓樹窩：偏僻到on9 個入口竟然係停車場上面 舊到乜咁<br />\n<br />\n長發：都係舊 健身又係細<br />\n<br />\n青衣西南：好大間 好新 但係竟然無健身室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n政府有無用過個腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623eb62cdc87ec46c0d02f1a18472b2355b27f77","tid":831893,"uid":61091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b60bc432ed2c4fdc8c4cc9a0f228932f0631464d","tid":831893,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:02:42.000Z","msg":"No<br />\n因為多公屋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:47:59.000Z","msg":"不過又係 除咗青衣城之外 都諗唔到邊個位可以開個gym room"},{"pid":"62790e05d8c3d028258f85b29bec0a9ebbb7739d","tid":831893,"uid":126326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T22:48:31.000Z","msg":"如果要開係市中心<br />\n